# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Re-include dashboard frontend source.
# The Python boilerplate above (`lib/`, `build/`, `dist/`, `project*`,
# `Project*`) is unanchored and silently swallows TypeScript source files
# under dashboard/frontend/src/ (e.g. src/lib/api.ts, src/app/projects/).
# This negation re-includes the entire frontend source tree so future
# files can't be quietly dropped from the build context.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
!dashboard/frontend/src/**
